Dwelling &lt;|-down- Commune: Inheritance
Dwelling &lt;|-down- House: Inheritance
Dwelling &quot;1&quot; *-up- &quot;many&quot; Window: Composition
Dwelling &quot;1&quot; *-up- &quot;many&quot; Door: Composition
&#123;% endplantuml %&#125;

